'''''Kbela''''', ni filime ngufi yo muri Berezile 2015 iyobowe na Yasmin Thayna  ikorwa na Princeton yo muri Berezile LAB<ref>https://kbela.org/</ref>.   Filime yibanze ku ivanguramoko ryinjira mu buzima bw'abagore b'abirabura muri [[Burezile|Berezile]].<ref>https://www.assistebrasil.com.br/direcoes/premiado-curta-kbela-de-yasmin-thayna-e-disponibilizado-online/</ref> 

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://iffr.com/en/iffr/2019/films/kbela</ref>.  Iyi filime yasohotse mu [[Buholandi]] ku ya 24 Mutarama 2019 mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime Rotterdam <ref>https://mubi.com/films/kbela</ref>. Ku ya 28 Ukwakira 2019, yasohotse mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya  Carolina y'Amajyaruguru, muri [[Amerika]]<ref>https://meiramonteiro.com/portfolio/kbela-leiamulheres/</ref>. Muri 2017, iyi filime yahawe igihembo cyiza cya [[Afurika]] Diaspora Igihembo cya [[Afurika]] cyatanzwe na Africa Movie Academy Awards (AMAA).<ref>http://www.goianiamostracurtas.com.br/18/personalidades/yasmin-thayna/</ref>   

